articles.author: Adam Cooper
articles.title: Wolff cautions against Mercedes "exuberance" after strong F1 qualifying - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Mercedes Formula 1 boss Toto Wolff has cautioned that the team shouldn't swing towards "exuberance" after a strong qualifying performance at the Australian GP.
